flowchart TD
    U[User] --> UI[Streamlit UI app.py]
    UI --> SESS[Session Manager]
    UI --> GEN[Quiz Generation Service]

    GEN --> RAG[RAG Quiz Pipeline]
    RAG --> EMB[Embedding Generator]
    EMB --> QV[(Query Vector)]
    QV --> CHQ[Chroma Query]
    CHQ --> VDB[(ChromaDB Persistent Store)]
    VDB --> HIST[Historical Retrieval Chunks]

    RAG --> NEWS[DuckDuckGo News Search]
    NEWS --> NRES[Latest News Results]

    HIST --> MERGE[Merge + Rank + Deduplicate Context]
    NRES --> MERGE
    MERGE --> PROMPT[Grounded Prompt Builder]
    PROMPT --> LLM[LLM Provider Gemini/OpenAI]
    LLM --> RAW[Raw Quiz JSON Text]

    RAW --> PARSE[Quiz Parser]
    PARSE --> VALID[Quiz Validator]
    VALID --> PAYLOAD[Quiz Payload]
    PAYLOAD --> UI
    UI --> SCORE[Answer Evaluation + Explanations + Sources]
